&lt;div class="container"&gt;
 &lt;div class="content"&gt;
 &lt;div class="title"&gt;KubeOps — dotnet-operator-sdk&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/dotnet/dotnet-operator-sdk" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;KubeOps&lt;/a&gt; is a Kubernetes Operator SDK for .NET, strongly inspired by kubebuilder. It enables developers to build production-grade Kubernetes operators using C# and ASP.NET Core — bridging the gap between the .NET ecosystem and Cloud Native infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contributing as collaborator since November 2025.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="meta"&gt;
 
 
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="date"&gt;2025&lt;/div&gt;
